=\"h3\" atcb_img=\"15\"]\r\n<ul class=\"point-list\">\r\n 	<li>HTML, HTML5, CSS</li>\r\n 	<li>SASS, Compass, GIT</li>\r\n 	<li>JavaScript, jQuery, many Javascript and jQuery libraries</li>\r\n 	<li>WordPress (including API), Bootstrap, Foundation</li>\r\n 	<li>PHP, MySQL</li>\r\n 	<li>Adobe Photoshop, Pixel Perfect</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/alio_three_columns_block]|[alio_three_columns_block atcb_title=\"In The End\" atcb_tag=\"h3\" atcb_img=\"14\"]\r\n<ul class=\"point-list\">\r\n 	<li>A ready functioning website with its admin panel on WordPress - most popular CMS in the world, by the way.</li>\r\n 	<li>Quality valid and clean code, optimized for search engines.</li>\r\n 	<li>Optimized graphics, images, ideal weight and quality for the web.</li>\r\n 	<li>High download speed - high Google Speed Test rate points.</li>\r\n 	<li>js-scripts based on jQuery, and WordPress plug-ins is installed and configured.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/alio_three_columns_block]|[alio_three_columns_block atcb_title=\"My approach\" atcb_tag=\"h3\" atcb_img=\"16\"]\r\n\r\nIn the approach to business I\'m a perfectionist, so pay special attention to the clean and structured of code, comments, literate class names. Assiduity and perseverance also helps me to achieve high-quality results. I always seeking to expand knowledge and strive to learn new technologies.\r\n\r\n[/alio_three_columns_block][/alio_three_columns_area][alio_divider ad_style=\"empty\" ad_bottom=\"50\"][alio_works_area awa_title=\"My Works\" awa_lnk_id=\"works\" awa_count_posts=\"-1\" awa_section=\"gray\"][alio_divider ad_style=\"empty\" ad_bottom=\"50\"][alio_text_block atb_lnk_id=\"how\" atb_title=\"How to order Website Development?\"]\r\n\r\nTo order Website Development, redesign (transferring website to a WordPress from other CMS platform), web layout, simply complete the form <a class=\"inline-lnk\" href=\"#lnk_order-form\">below</a>. On the issues of SEO and marketing do not disturb! Only work with CMS WordPress. For the work with Joomla, Bitrix, Drupal ect. - do not disturb! It is advisable to send a psd-layout or screenshot of the project so that I could appreciate the complexity of the work and immediately tell You the time and cost of development. In the near future I will contact You, and in correspondence then agreed everything controversial and further questions.\r\n\r\n[/alio_text_block][alio_divider ad_style=\"empty\" ad_bottom=\"50\"][alio_form_block afb_lnk_id=\"order-form\" afb_title=\"Order Website Development\" afb_section=\"odd\" afb_additional_class=\"order-form\" afb_bottom_shape=\"no-wave\"][contact-form-7 id=\"121\" title=\"Wesbite order\"][/alio_form_block][alio_divider ad_style=\"empty\" ad_bottom=\"50\"][:]', '[:ru]Алио. Неистовый кодинг[:en]Furious coding from Alio[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-18 17:41:58', '2018-08-18 14:41:58', '', 11, 'http://frantic-coding.000webhostapp.com/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
