der-form\">below</a>. On the issues of SEO and marketing do not disturb! Only work with CMS WordPress. For the work with Joomla, Bitrix, Drupal ect. - do not disturb! It is advisable to send a psd-layout or screenshot of the project so that I could appreciate the complexity of the work and immediately tell You the time and cost of development. In the near future I will contact You, and in correspondence then agreed everything controversial and further questions.\r\n\r\n[/alio_text_block][alio_divider ad_style=\"empty\" ad_bottom=\"50\"][alio_form_block afb_lnk_id=\"order-form\" afb_title=\"Order Website Development\" afb_section=\"odd\" afb_additional_class=\"order-form\" afb_bottom_shape=\"no-wave\"][contact-form-7 id=\"121\" title=\"Wesbite order\"][/alio_form_block][alio_divider ad_style=\"empty\" ad_bottom=\"50\"][:]', '[:ru]Алио. Неистовый кодинг[:en]Furious coding from Alio[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-11 11:39:31', '2019-07-11 08:39:31', '', 11, 'http://frantic-coding.000webhostapp.com/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
