like Gulp, Webpack, and Git don&rsquo;t scare&nbsp;me. You can find my&nbsp;detailed resume on&nbsp;the link <a href=\"https://hh.ru/resume/1c0c0095ff0271c0380039ed1f756b64654a6c\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here (hh)</a>.</p>\r\n<p>I&nbsp;am an&nbsp;active member of&nbsp;the Russian WordPress community. Repeatedly participated in&nbsp;the organization of&nbsp;WordPress meetaps in&nbsp;Omsk city, also has experience of&nbsp;public speaking as&nbsp;a&nbsp;speaker. Also I&nbsp;participated in&nbsp;the development of&nbsp;the world open source WordPress community by&nbsp;writing plug-ins for this CMS. Some of&nbsp;these plugins are presented among my&nbsp;works <a class=\"inline-lnk\" href=\"#lnk_works\">below</a>.</p>\r\n<p>I&nbsp;strive to&nbsp;expand accumulated knowledge, learning for new technologies and apply it&nbsp;in&nbsp;developing high-quality websites and WordPress plugins.</p>\r\n<p>At&nbsp;the moment, I&nbsp;have already designed and configured many sites of&nbsp;various subjects and complexity. Some of&nbsp;them are presented <a class=\"inline-lnk\" href=\"#lnk_works\">below</a>.</p>[/alio_text_block][alio_divider ad_style=\"wave\" ad_top=\"50\" ad_bottom=\"30\"][alio_three_columns_area atca_lnk_id=\"skills\" atca_title=\"What do I offer\"][alio_three_columns_block atcb_title=\"WordPress Design & Development\" atcb_tag=\"h3\" atcb_img=\"15\"]\r\n<ul class=\"point-list\">\r\n    <li>Templated websites for the budget-conscious</li>\r\n    <li>Custom built websites made to&nbsp;your design</li>\r\n    <li>Custom WordPress themes</li>\r\n    <li>Custom functionality and WordPress plugins</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a class=\"alio-btn\" href=\"#lnk_order-form\">Order now</a>\r\n[/alio_three_columns_block]|[alio_three_columns_block atcb_title=\"WordPress Maintenance\" atcb_tag=\"h3\" atcb_img=\"14\"]\r\n<ul class=\"point-list\">\r\n    <li>From backups to&nbsp;updates, we&nbsp;do&nbsp;it&nbsp;all:</li>\r\n    <li>Performance optimization</li>\r\n    <li>Updates installation</li>\r\n    <li>Malware removal</li>\r\n    <li>Automated backups</li>\r\n    <li>Security audit and monitoring</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a class=\"alio-btn\" href=\"#lnk_order-form\">Order now</a>\r\n[/alio_three_columns_block]|[alio_three_columns_block atcb_title=\"Complex WordPress solutions\" atcb_tag=\"h3\" atcb_img=\"16\"]\r\n<ul class=\"point-list\">\r\n    <li>We&nbsp;like to&nbsp;push the limits of&nbsp;what is possible to&nbsp;build with WordPress:</li>\r\n    <li>3rd party API integrations</li>\r\n    <li>WordPress multisite setup</li>\r\n    <li>eCommerce solutions</li>\r\n    <li>Custom functionality</li>\r\n    <li>Various automations</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a class=\"alio-btn\" href=\"#lnk_order-form\">Order now</a>\r\n[/alio_three_columns_block][/alio_three_columns_area][alio_divider ad_style=\"wave\" ad_bottom=\"30\"][alio_text_block atb_lnk_id=\"\" atb_title=\"P.S.\"]\r\n<p>I&nbsp;do not do&nbsp;SEO optimization and site promotion. HTML-layout can be&nbsp;done from scratch (on&nbsp;the PSD layout), and make edits and bring to&nbsp;mind the pages already laid out by&nbsp;someone. I&nbsp;also do&nbsp;a&nbsp;so-called site redesign using themes and WordPress templates.</p>\r\n<p>Having dealt with&nbsp;me, you can be&nbsp;sure of&nbsp;my&nbsp;responsiveness to&nbsp;you, literacy of&nbsp;approach, sanity and responsibility in&nbsp;carrying out the Technical Assignment. Feel free to&nbsp;contact&nbsp;us today is&nbsp;a&nbsp;great day for our cooperation. <a class=\"inline-lnk\" href=\"#lnk_order-form\">Go?</a></p>\r\n[/alio_text_block][alio_divider ad_style=\"empty\" ad_bottom=\"50\"][alio_works_area awa_title=\"My works\" awa_lnk_id=\"works\" awa_count_posts=\"-1\" awa_section=\"gray\"][alio_divider ad_style=\"empty\" ad_bottom=\"50\"][alio_text_block atb_lnk_id=\"how\" atb_title=\"How to order Website Development?\"]\r\n<p>To&nbsp;order Website Development, redesign (transferring website to&nbsp;a&nbsp;WordPress from other CMS platform), web layout, simply complete the form <a class=\"inline-lnk\" href=\"#lnk_order-form\">below</a>. On&nbsp;the issues of&nbsp;SEO and marketing do&nbsp;not disturb! Only work with CMS WordPress. For the work with Joomla, Bitrix, Drupal ect. &mdash;&nbsp;do&nbsp;not disturb! It&nbsp;is&nbsp;advisable to&nbsp;send a&nbsp;psd-layout or&nbsp;screenshot of&nbsp;the project so&nbsp;that&nbsp;I could appreciate the complexity of&nbsp;the work and immediately tell You the time and cost of&nbsp;development. In&nbsp;the near future&nbsp;I will contact You, and in&nbsp;correspondence then agreed everything controversial and further questions.</p>\r\n[/alio_text_block][alio_divider ad_style=\"empty\" ad_bottom=\"50\"][alio_form_block afb_lnk_id=\"order-form\" afb_title=\"Order Website Development\" afb_section=\"odd\" afb_additional_class=\"order-form\" afb_bottom_shape=\"no-wave\"][contact-form-7 id=\"121\" title=\"Wesbite order\"][/alio_form_block][:]', '[:ru]Алио. Неистовый кодинг[:en]Furious coding from Alio[:]', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-23 13:19:18', '2019-07-23 10:19:18', '', 11, 'http://frantic-coding.000webhostapp.com/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
